deck_excerpt: #blue-eyes #with eyes of blue #dragon master magia #ultimaate spirit dragon
deck_description: Fun little blue-eyes that tries to stick to the theme of the card as much as possible. If Master Magia is not an option for you, remove it, blue-eyes ultimate dragon, chaos max and ultimate fusion and put the 2 triple tactics on the main deck and Lyna and Heavenly Spheres on the extra deck. Other staples are also viable for the deck, such as Little Knight and Mulcharmy Fuwaross, but I tried to keep the deck on a reasonable budget (I'm considering Master Magia at his actual reasonable price). You can add those if you want and have the money for it, but the deck completely works without them so you don't have to feel any pressure to do it.
